{
  "texts": [
    "Information extraction in languages other than English has its own challenges [39].",
    "In the case of the Spanish language, there is a lack of approaches to performing clinical NER, given the limited availability of annotated data.",
    "These approaches could have an impact on information extraction in the medical domain.",
    "Furthermore, it has yet to be explored to use LLMs to perform and evaluate clinical NER in Spanish.",
    "Problem statementExtracting information from EHRs using machine learning models requires the availability of labeled datasets."
  ]
}